<item>
            <title>[LU-11994] Add support for LSOM in LFSCK</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11994</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;From Andreas:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It makes sense to enhance LFSCK to update the LSOM size during a scan so that it is available and accurate for all existing files.  Ideally, it should convert LSOM into strict SOM for all files, so &lt;tt&gt;stat()&lt;/tt&gt; on clients do not need to access the OST objects at all.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="54963">LU-11994</key>
            <summary>Add support for LSOM in LFSCK</summary>
                <type id="4" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11310&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Improvement</type>
